<h3 id='error-code'>Error Code</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Code</th>
<th>Message</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>400</td>
<td><code>ALREADY_VERIFIED_PHONE</code></td>
<td>이미 인증된 전화번호</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>400</td>
<td><code>INVALID_VERIFICATION_CODE</code></td>
<td>유효하지 않은 인증 코드</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>401</td>
<td><code>VERIFICATION_CODE_UNAVAILABLE_OR_EXPIRED</code></td>
